# Client-side build-time vars. Baked into the Expo web bundle; gitignored as
# .env. The deploy script (scripts/push_and_deploy.sh) rsyncs this file to
# the target before `npm run build:web` runs.
#
# Mercury-pilot is mounted under the /pilot path on the iMac's Tailscale
# Funnel (https://marxs-imac.tail876aa7.ts.net/pilot). All API calls from
# the web bundle need to target that same prefix — tailscale strips it
# before forwarding so Express still handles plain /api/* on :3002.
#
# For local dev (no tailscale), set this empty or comment it out:
#   EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=
# For prod (matches the tailscale serve set-path):
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=/pilot
